posting_body: ['Property Address', '1329 Grand Ave - 9 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Historic Studio at The Summit View Apartments', 'This back corner studio on the second floor features a Northwest view looking out to Summit Avenue.', 'At 500 square feet, this spacious studio features wood floors, an eat-in kitchen, and the charm of the classic brownstone Grand Avenue apartments.', 'Schedule your showing now as this apartment will not last long!', 'Atop the Grand & Summit Avenue ridge, the Summit View Apartments feature the classic brownstone look while also offering the desired blend of modern convenience.', 'Located on the corner of Grand and Hamline Avenue, our Summit View Apartments offer the proximity to the shops and dining all along Grand Avenue and to the major roads in the Twin Cities.', 'Ask about our off-street parking availability.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Heat Water Trash & Recycling Paid', '24-hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Cats Welcome', 'Fitness Center and Clubhouse', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 500', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $890.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
